      <title>欧盟因克里姆林宫在 Facebook、Instagram 上撒谎而面临罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/meta-risks-eu-fines-over-kremlin-lies-on-facebook-instagram</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 的社交媒体平台 Facebook 和 Instagram 正在接受欧盟的调查，原因是担心它们未能剔除俄罗斯散布的旨在在欧洲大陆煽动不和的有针对性的虚假信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/meta-risks-eu-fines-over-kremlin-lies-on-facebook-instagram</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 10:00:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能热潮推动谷歌首席执行官桑达尔·皮查伊 (Sundar Pichai) 接近亿万富翁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/google-ceo-sundar-pichai-nears-billionaire-status-powered-by-ai-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alphabet Inc. 首席执行官桑达尔·皮查伊 (Sundar Pichai) 即将实现非创始人科技高管罕见的里程碑：十位数财富。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/google-ceo-sundar-pichai-nears-billionaire-status-powered-by-ai-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华为在中国利润飙升564% 超越苹果</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/huawei-profit-surges-564-as-it-eclipses-apple-in-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华为技术有限公司的利润连续第四个季度增长，这表明这家中国科技公司正在从苹果公司和其他智能手机竞争对手手中夺取市场份额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/huawei-profit-surges-564-as-it-eclipses-apple-in-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 09:39:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>RedBird IMI 在英国遭遇强烈反对后开始出售 Telegraph</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/redbird-imi-kicks-off-sale-of-telegraph-after-uk-backlash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在经历了几个月的痛苦之后，阿联酋支持的投资者 RedBird IMI 正在放弃收购《电讯报》报纸和《Spectator》杂志的尝试，并将考虑出售其对英国媒体的权利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/redbird-imi-kicks-off-sale-of-telegraph-after-uk-backlash</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 08:33:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能蓬勃发展，台湾经济以 2021 年以来最快速度增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/taiwan-economy-grows-at-fastest-pace-since-2021-on-chip-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球对人工智能相关技术的需求推动了出口的繁荣，台湾经济以近三年来最快的速度增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/taiwan-economy-grows-at-fastest-pace-since-2021-on-chip-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 08:07:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 法将如何加剧中美科技争端</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/how-the-tiktok-law-could-intensify-the-us-china-tech-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该法律几乎肯定会导致最高法院提起诉讼，并对美国在中国的利益进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/how-the-tiktok-law-could-intensify-the-us-china-tech-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 08:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SES 同意以 31 亿美元的卫星交易收购 Intelsat</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/ses-agrees-to-buy-intelsat-in-3-1-billion-satellite-deal-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在重启去年破裂的谈判后，SES SA 同意以 31 亿美元现金收购 Intelsat SA，以打造一家卫星巨头，更好地与亿万富翁埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的星链 (Starlink) 竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/ses-agrees-to-buy-intelsat-in-3-1-billion-satellite-deal-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 07:01:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰雷兹首席财务官表示，如果出售 Atos Defence 部门，泰雷兹有兴趣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/thales-interested-in-atos-defense-unit-if-put-on-sale-cfo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国国防集团首席财务官 Pascal Bouchiat 表示，泰雷兹公司对属于 Atos SE 大数据和安全部门一部分的国防业务感兴趣，如果该业务出售的话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/thales-interested-in-atos-defense-unit-if-put-on-sale-cfo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 06:40:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国锂业先锋在损失后将控制权交给女儿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/china-lithium-giant-s-founder-hands-reins-to-daughter-after-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国主要锂生产商天齐锂业的创始人蒋卫平在这家电池材料生产商公布有史以来最大季度亏损超过 5 亿美元后辞去了董事长职务。]]></description>
